From Future Dreams to Intimacy, explore over 13 categories designed to spark conversation. You answer honestly, your partner guesses your answer to see who knows who best. It turns serious relationship building into a fun, low-pressure game.

Location tracking app is a GPS tracker that helps you locate your family, kids, friends, loved ones, and people you care about in real time on a live, shared, and private map.  

Smart Circles
With Smart Circles, you can create a circle of people who all share their locations within the group and can track each others location history and location in real time. Invite group members by sharing a unique, private 6-digit number. After the invitations are accepted, you can find people in your circle easily at any time.

Geo-fence zones
Use geozones to know which of your circle members are in a certain area the moment they arrive. Setting up is easy: first, drop a pin on the map to set the center of the geo-fence at a specific location. Next, name your geolocation, set the radius for it, and once it's created, you'll know when your circle members enter and exit it by getting push notifications. Geo zones automatically let you know where your loved ones are without any effort from them — for example, you can create a geo-fence at your children's school to tell you they've arrived safely, or create one around your home to alert you when a family member is about to arrive.

Emergency SOS function
In trouble? By tapping on the SOS button, all members of your circles will get an urgent push notification that you need help, with a live update of where you are. You can feel secure in your life knowing your child, partner, or friend can alert you any time they are lost, in danger, or need help.

Other features:
- Find your family and friends on the mobile map in real time.
- View location history of each circle member.
- 'Find my device' by GPS phone tracker in case your device is lost.
- Manage group circles and geo-fence zones.
- More features are coming soon!

Kidsee is your trusted assistant in parental control.

It is an innovative app designed to keep your children safe and give you control over their use of mobile devices. A handy screen time tracker that helps parents see how much time their child spends playing games, using apps, and on social media. Kidsee allows you to set time limits for your children across various apps and games.

Key features:  
- Monitoring multiple devices: You can now track screen time and digital activity not just for one child, but for multiple children at the same time. Manage all your children's devices from a single parent phone by creating individual profiles for each child and setting personalised limits for each device.  
- Location tracking: Monitor your child's real-time location and view their route history to ensure their safety.  
- Device synchronisation: Connect your child's devices to yours to access the information you need. Create and edit their profiles to customise settings for each child.  
- Set time limits: Define time limits for phone use by day of the week to maintain a balance between fun and responsibilities.  
- Block apps: Block unwanted apps so your child can focus on schoolwork and other important tasks.  
- Usage statistics: View detailed app usage statistics to understand your child's digital habits. Know which apps your child is using, at what time, and for how long.  
- Motivational tasks: Create useful tasks for your child — for example, finish homework, tidy their room, or help their younger sibling. When children complete tasks, they earn extra screen time, which helps shape responsible behaviour and encourages good habits.  
- Push notifications: Receive notifications when usage time limits are reached to stay up to date with your child's activity.

Kidsee is your trusted assistant in creating a safe and balanced digital world for kids! Installing Kidsee is an important step towards fostering responsible technology users.

Download Kidsee and provide your children with a safe digital environment!

Welcome to Kidsee!
